Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.72,0:01:06.22,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}赞颂你的内心吧
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.49,0:01:12.08,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}淡淡的小花们
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.41,0:01:17.22,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}坚韧不挠的藤蔓的形状
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.88,0:01:22.64,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}怀中藏有刺的影子
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.11,0:01:29.62,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}各自怀着不可言喻的昨天
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.62,0:01:33.37,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}向天空而去
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.77,0:01:38.83,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}只要生命还在  就喊出愿望吧
